Package: nvbenchr
Type: Package
Title: R bindings for NVBench CUDA benchmarking library
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Ziyad", family = "AlBanoby", email = "zalbanoby@bsc.es", role = c("aut","ctb","cre"))
  )
Description: R interface to the NVBench CUDA benchmarking library mirroring the
    Python bindings shipped with this repository. Benchmarks are registered from R
    functions and executed through the NVBench engine.
License: Apache License (>= 2.0) with LLVM exception
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: CUDA toolkit, NVBench
Imports: R6, Rcpp (>= 1.0.11)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
